data.description: Come and take a look at that this charming home located in the heart of town! The cute, covered porch welcomes you into this cozy country home. This home features beautiful original hardwood floors, gas fireplace, recently redone main bath, downstairs master bedroom, dual water heaters, firepit and 15x15 shop! Located in quiet neighborhood and walking distance to all schools.  Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from county records .  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
